## Graph DB Settings: Cascading Lakebase + UC Pickers — 2026-05-12

### Context
Settings → Graph DB now offers a guided, cascading selection flow for Lakebase configuration
instead of a single free-text database field. Admins can discover the available Autoscaling
projects, then drill down to branches → databases → Postgres schemas. For Managed Sync,
the UC catalog picker now triggers a UC schema picker (previously only catalog was selectable).
A new `sync_uc_schema` config key stores the UC schema separately from the catalog.

### Changes

1. `src/back/core/graphdb/lakebase/LakebaseBase.py`
