|---|---|
| Postgres `_sync` table | `ontobricks_graph` schema |
| Postgres companion table | `ontobricks_graph` schema |
| Postgres union view | `ontobricks_graph` schema |
| UC synced-table FQN | `benoit_cayla.ontobricks_graph.<table>` |

